-how to do first time discovery of nodes
 first: define all service types from UI
 second:run FirstTimeDiscovery/discoverServicesOnAllInventoryNodes.php

-how to do frequent discovery at the background instead of in house( NetworkServiceHandler::handleServiceQuery: using $isAsynchProcessInPlace=false)

 first make sure $isAsynchProcessInPlace is set to true
 setup Setup a cron with frequent execution (such as every 30 secs) using:
  ContinousDiscovery\updateServiceSegmentsSingleNode.cron.php


